    <p><em class="focus">Numra</em> is a program for practicing numerals. We recommend Numra to all students of Saami: In order to learn a language you must know its numeral system.</p>

<section><title>Options</title>
<ul>
<li>Range: 0-10, 0-20, 0-100 or 0-1000.</li>
<li>Mode: From number to numeral, and from numeral to number.</li>
<li>Ordinal numbers.</li>
<li>Time</li>
<li>Dates</li>
</ul>


</section>


